author: Warhammer
description:
Buri Aegnirssen surges into the foe with the ferocious abandon of one who has nothing left to lose. With sweeps of his adaptable darkstar glaive, this survivor carves a bloody path through the enemy. Tune in to this paint guide to see Ollie show you how to quickly and easily paint this epic Leagues of Votann character!

Here’s a list of the paints we used in today’s video:

Base:
Corax White
Corvus Black
Grey Seer
Iron Warriors
Naggaroth Night
Mechanicus Standard Grey
Retributor Armour
Rhinox Hide
Stegadon Scale Green
Wraithbone

Layer:
Genestealer Purple
Ulthuan Grey
Slaanesh Grey
Stormhost Silver
Fenrisian Grey

Shade:
Coelia Greenshade
Druchii Violet
Targor Rageshade

Contrast:
Blood Angels Red
Frostheart
Magos Purple
Sigvald Burgundy

Technical:
Contrast Medium

Tools:
S Layer
M Layer
S Dry
L Base
M Shade

If you enjoyed this and want to learn more, our YouTube channel has an array of beginner-friendly videos to get you started.

Follow for more Warhammer, more often:

- Instagram
title: How To Paint Buri Aegnirssen | Warhammer 40,000
